10/05/2004
TIRANA, Albania -- EU ambassadors and other representatives of the diplomatic corps in Albania called on the government Saturday (8 May) to accelerate reforms. They emphasised that this is the only way the country will proceed on the road to EU integration. The diplomats also stressed the need for electoral reforms to ensure fair and free elections in 2005, including a reshaping of the Central Electoral Commission. (ATA - 08/05/04)
